{"tid":1605414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求求大家簽一簽佢","createTime":"2019-09-30T09:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:38:19.000Z","uid":70781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3558ad8b58ecff413842db8b8bad830b5f22ffca","tid":1605414,"uid":70781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"路透社報道，英國外相 Dominic Raab 指出，英國脫歐後就會立一條類似美國《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》嘅法案，對任何違反人權嘅士予以制裁，包括禁止入境、凍結相關個人（或者組織）的財產。<br />\n<br />\n所以你使乜為每一個冚家剷開一個聯署？我哋集中請美國行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》好過啦，制裁中共及相關人等已經係國際大趨勢嘞。<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n白宮聯署（10月10日到期）<br />\n請美國政府行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/global-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fglobal-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=96f0c4ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/global-magnitsky-act-pro-beijing-officials-hong-kong-executive-council</a><br />\n<br />\n簽＞查電郵＞確認簽署＞廣傳<br />\n<br />\n新聞出處：<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-britain-eu-raab/britain-to-introduce-a-magnitsky-law-after-brexit-foreign-minister-idUSKBN1WE0IT?fbclid=IwAR3U9Q1XP-E1oNx-q9ixk2VtvnzXP8iLJGUjKIwblZFQ4vv0KiIoUuPoT5c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-britain-eu-raab%2Fbritain-to-introduce-a-magnitsky-law-after-brexit-foreign-minister-idUSKBN1WE0IT%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3U9Q1XP-E1oNx-q9ixk2VtvnzXP8iLJGUjKIwblZFQ4vv0KiIoUuPoT5c&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZvGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=c094e4dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-britain-eu-raab%2Fbritain-to-introduce-a-magnitsky-law-after-brexit-foreign-minister-idUSKBN1WE0IT%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3U9Q1XP-E1oNx-q9ixk2VtvnzXP8iLJGUjKIwblZFQ4vv0KiIoUuPoT5c&h=05c26b28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-britain-eu-raab/britain-to-introduce-a-magnitsky-law-after-brexit-foreign-minister-idUSKBN1WE0IT?fbclid=IwAR3U9Q1XP-E1oNx-q9ixk2VtvnzXP8iLJGUjKIwblZFQ4vv0KiIoUuPoT5c</a>"},{"pid":"91d8daeeafbfafd24cec3632c13761dca0ca5b98","tid":1605414,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:38:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}